  Now I know we all would like to have the perfect groups for a Planer Raid, but, my question is this.<br>
<br>
 For Fear,based on the number of Enchanters you have, what is the LEAST you would go ahead on a Fear raid with?<br>
<br>
 I have been to 2 Fear Raids one had 4, the last only had 2.<br>
Now ,I dont know how many of you know what an Enchanter's role entails..But, we give clarity,Sltw&gt;Swift Like the Wind,Rune, Insight,Brilliance,Single mez and crowd mez,Theft of thought, Tash, we have a line of Stuns..Group MR and a line of bebuffers.<br>
<br>
 So, would you, go ahead with a raid that only had 2 enchanters for Fear??without thinking it was a suicide mission? hehe and please,can I have some honest answers,and not ego ones..and how much importance  do you place on your Enchanters on what they can handle..i.e. When i say I  can't handle all this, it's not to say  I am complaining of the workload,BUT..for realistic reasons I, as an Enchanter do not think I can best serve my team AND to be able to say I had a good time when over half the time I am doing CR, due to fizzles, resist's and someone breaking mez and the mob come after me,or being OOM and the people sending me tells for clarity or speed  think I just pull the mana out of my pocket<br>
<br>
   Anyway, some honest answers and not ridicule, would be very much appreciated. <p>Adenia Reviel 51th Illusionist<BR>Second in Command and Recruiting Officer of<BR>Twilight Marauders</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#313532><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon2.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/unadiabrell.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nadia brell</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Traveller of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 233<br> <font color=#CC9900>(5/4/01 4:24:01 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> <BR><img src=http://home.earthlink.net/~karl23/_images/nadia60.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: The Best Team., the Worst team for a Fear raid</span><hr size=1> I've been on many Fear raids where there was only 1 enchanter<br>
<br>
I've been on some Fear raids where there was NO ENCHANTER<br>
<br>
No enchanter just makes it more challenging, nothing more. <p>Nadia Nightengale<BR>
Weekend Enchantress<BR>
Blood Inferno<BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uelkanir.showPublicProfile?language=EN>elkanir</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot</span><br>  Posts: 43<br> <font color=#CC9900>(5/4/01 4:25:49 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: The Best Team., the Worst team for a Fear raid</span><hr size=1> 2 chanter is good for fear <br>
one do buff (clarity speed) the other is in pull and do some mez<br>
